Summary: 

 * Merge from SystemC-Examples--mainline--0.2 Branch
 
 * Added subdirectory systemc-mpeg4-teich-v2 for Prof. Teich
 - systemc-mpeg4-teich-v2 should be used to test the xslt converter
 - The toplevel design is constructed in systemc-mpeg4-teich-v2/design-mpeg4-teich.cpp
 - The xslt generated code belongs into systemc-mpeg4-teich-v2/Video_XML
 - The code in Video_XML should be included in the design-mpeg4-teich.cpp file
 - The network graph of the actors should be constructed in design-mpeg4-teich.cpp
   an example network graph for the an IDCT2d test is included in the
   design-mpeg4-teich.cpp file.

 * Added addTransition example in design-mpeg4-teich.cpp
 - addTransition example is in the constructors of the m_source and m_sink actors

 * Changes in some actors (cal:col2block) as well as all generated files *out.xml;
   also README adapted in systemc-mpeg4-teich-v2 to final possibilities for extensions;
   Finally, also changed file callib.hpp to allow for bitand and bitor operations;

 * Actor col2block.cal changed so not to use list concatenation operators! 

 * All files except 1 error in File parser, 2 errors in reconstruct and 1 error in file MCadd
            (initList) compile without errors with version Teich17.xslt

 * Fixed systemc-mpeg4/configuration.cmx.xml to correspond
   to the changed problem graph in design-test-idct2d.cpp
   which arose by  merging the two source actors src and src1
   into a new src_idct actor.

